The '''Bror Towers''' were a collection of skyscrapers located on the planet [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Each tower stood more than 150 stories tall, and all were linked by a series of walkways between towers. Much of the interior space of the Towers was given over to art exhibits and museums.

